    "title": "Job Opening Teacher at T.I.M.E.",
    "description": "Join the T.I.M.E. family as a Teacher in Gurgaon. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout T.I.M.E.:\nT.I.M.E. is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Design formative and summative assessments aligned to learning objectives\n• Participate in school events, workshops, and training programs\n• Coordinate with academic counselors for student career guidance\n• Monitor student progress and provide timely feedback\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n• Utilize technology and digital tools to enhance learning outcomes\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Student Assessment\n• Proficiency in Special Education\n• Proficiency in CBSE/ICSE Standards\n• Proficiency in Data Analysis\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in Lesson Planning\n• Proficiency in Zoom/Teams\n• Proficiency in Child Psychology\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Flexible working hours\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gurgaon, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with T.I.M.E.!",
